Detailed Description

The following Pitches across 8 octaves are defined with global scope.



Const Pitch C0, C1, ..., C7, C natural in all piano octaves
Const Pitch Cs0, Cs1, ..., Cs7, C sharp (D flat) in all piano octaves
Const Pitch Db0, Db1, ..., Db7, D flat (C sharp) in all piano octaves
Const Pitch D0, D1, ..., D7, D natural in all piano octaves
...

The Pitches implemented are C*, Cs*, Db*, D*, Eb*, E*, F*, Fs*, Gb*, G*, Gs*, Ab*, A*, As*, Bb*, B* where * is any piano octave in the range [0,7]
